 SOURCE CODE: # to check whether number entered is positive,negative or zero. 
 num = input(&quot;Enter a number :&quot;) 
 if int(num) == 0: print(&quot; entered number is 0.&quot;)
 elif int(num)&lt;0: print(&quot; entered number is a negative number.&quot;) 
 else: print(&quot; entered number is a positive number.&quot;) 
 
 OUTPUT:
 Enter a number :50
 entered number is a positive number.
